From: Razvan Stefanescu <razvan.stefanescu@nxp.com>
Date: Thu, 14 Jun 2018 15:17:21 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 663/741] ocelot: Use all 8 flood masks for felix

commit 84bb2e741b287d48408e5e7bc3b2f5c0a0beb54b from
http://source.codeaurora.org/external/qoriq/qoriq-components/linux

A unicast or multicast frame with unknown DMAC is flooded to
all ports except the ingress port. But if only set flood masks
of queue 0, frames classified to 1-7 queues will be dropped.

Signed-off-by: Razvan Stefanescu <razvan.stefanescu@nxp.com>
Signed-off-by: Xiaoliang Yang <xiaoliang.yang_1@nxp.com>
Signed-off-by: Zhantao Tang <zhantao.tang@windriver.com>
---
 drivers/net/ethernet/mscc/ocelot.c | 10 ++++++----
 1 file changed, 6 insertions(+), 4 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/net/ethernet/mscc/ocelot.c b/drivers/net/ethernet/mscc/ocelot.c
index 90dd5615925e..6ef0cd19eb66 100644
--- a/drivers/net/ethernet/mscc/ocelot.c
+++ b/drivers/net/ethernet/mscc/ocelot.c
@@ -1846,10 +1846,12 @@ int ocelot_init(struct ocelot *ocelot)
 		     SYS_FRM_AGING_MAX_AGE(307692), SYS_FRM_AGING);
 
 	/* Setup flooding PGIDs */
-	ocelot_write_rix(ocelot, ANA_FLOODING_FLD_MULTICAST(PGID_MC) |
-			 ANA_FLOODING_FLD_BROADCAST(PGID_MC) |
-			 ANA_FLOODING_FLD_UNICAST(PGID_UC),
-			 ANA_FLOODING, 0);
+	for (i = 0; i < 8; i++)
+		ocelot_write_rix(ocelot, ANA_FLOODING_FLD_MULTICAST(PGID_MC) |
+				 ANA_FLOODING_FLD_BROADCAST(PGID_MC) |
+				 ANA_FLOODING_FLD_UNICAST(PGID_UC),
+				 ANA_FLOODING, i);
+
 	ocelot_write(ocelot, ANA_FLOODING_IPMC_FLD_MC6_DATA(PGID_MCIPV6) |
 		     ANA_FLOODING_IPMC_FLD_MC6_CTRL(PGID_MC) |
 		     ANA_FLOODING_IPMC_FLD_MC4_DATA(PGID_MCIPV4) |
